Package: RandallRecipes
Title: Recipe Data Exploration
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Destini", "Randall", email = "destinirandall@yahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides a dataset of recipes and uses functions for filtering, comparing, and visualizing them. Users can search for specific recipes, generate random ones, and filter them based on ingredients or time. There is also a function allowing users to graph recipes and compare their characteristics. This package is intended for culinary students, chefs, and anyone interested in exploring recipe data.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr, stringr
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
